							</p>
						</provenance>
						<acquisition>
							<date>1853-11-12</date>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Adolphus Asher</name>: (b. 1800, d. 1853), Berlin bookseller and dealer to the British Museum (see <ref target="Paisey_1997" type="page">131-153</ref>: purchased from him on 12 November 1853: inscribed (folio [107v]).</p>
						</acquisition>
